members.name: IDBVersionChangeEvent.oldVersion
members.description: Returns the old version of the database.

members.name: IDBVersionChangeEvent.newVersion
members.description: Returns the new version of the database.

members.name: IDBVersionChangeEvent.version
members.description: The new version of the database in a versionchange transaction. Warning: While this property is still implemented in older browsers, the latest specification replaces it with the oldVersion and newVersion attributes. See the compatibility table to know what browsers support them.
